            "id": 9668664,
            "app_id": 100468,
            "parent_sub_control_id": null,
            "sub_control_template_id": 4555,
            "title": "Backup Audit Trail Files",
            "description": "<div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Overview:<\/b><\/div>Ensure the organization promptly backs up audit trail files to a centralized log server or media that is difficult to alter. Promptly backing up the logs to a centralized log server or media that is difficult to alter keeps the logs protected even if the system generating the logs becomes compromised.<br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Action Items:<\/b><\/div>1) Verify this control requirement is documented and known by all personnel. <br \/>\n2) Verify the organization promptly backs up audit trail files to a centralized log server or media that is difficult to alter.<br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Related Documents<\/b> <span>(document name and content will vary by organization):<\/span><\/div>1) Logging &amp; Monitoring Standard<br \/>\n2) Audit &amp; Access Control Policy<br \/>\n3) List of all backup locations for audit trail files",
