            "parent_sub_control_id": null,
            "sub_control_template_id": 4562,
            "title": "DHCP Logging",
            "description": "<div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Overview:<\/b><\/div>Use Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol (DHCP) logging on all DHCP servers or IP address management tools to update the organization's hardware asset inventory and help detect unknown systems. <br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Action Items:<\/b><\/div>1) Verify this control requirement is documented and known by all personnel. <br \/>\n2) Verify that the organization uses Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol (DHCP) logging on all DHCP servers or IP address management tools to update the organization's hardware asset inventory and help detect unknown systems<br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Related Documents<\/b> <span>(document name and content will vary by organization):<\/span><\/div>1) Logging &amp; Monitoring Standard<br \/>\n2) Audit &amp; Access Control Policy<br \/>\n3) Hardware Asset Inventory",
