            "app_id": 100468,
            "parent_sub_control_id": null,
            "sub_control_template_id": 4554,
            "title": "Limit Viewing of Audit Trail Files",
            "description": "<div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Overview:<\/b><\/div>Ensure that the organization limits viewing of audit trails to those with a job-related need. Adequate protection of the audit logs includes strong access control (limit access to logs based on &ldquo;need to know&rdquo; only), and use of physical or network segregation to make the logs harder to find and modify. <br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Action Items:<\/b><\/div>1) Verify that only individuals who have a job-related need can view audit trail files. <br \/>\n2) Verify this control requirement is documented and known by all personnel. <br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Related Documents<\/b> <span>(document name and content will vary by organization):<\/span><\/div>1) Logging &amp; Monitoring Standard<br \/>\n2) Audit &amp; Access Control Policy<br \/>\n3) List of individuals or roles who can view audit trail files.",
