            "sub_control_template_id": 4542,
            "title": "DNS Query Logging",
            "description": "<div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Overview:<\/b><\/div>Enable Domain Name System (DNS) query logging to detect hostname lookups for known malicious domains. <br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Action Items:<\/b><\/div>1) Verify that the organization enables Domain Name System (DNS) query logging to detect hostname lookups for known malicious domains. <br \/>\n2) Verify this control requirement is documented and known by all parties.<br \/>\n<br\/><div class=\"sub-sub-head\"><b>Related Documents<\/b> <span>(document name and content will vary by organization):<\/span><\/div>1) Logging &amp; Monitoring Standard<br \/>\n2) Audit and Accountability Policy<br \/>\n3) Logs of all DNS queries",
